The Beach Boys appear as performers in the [[beach party films]] ''[[The Girls on the Beach]]'' (1965) and ''[[The Monkey's Uncle]]'' (1965). They have also made [[cameo appearance]]s in the television series ''[[Full House]]'' (1988–1992), ''[[Home Improvement (TV series)|Home Improvement]]'' (1993), and ''[[Baywatch]]'' (1995).{{citation needed|date=June 2015}}

The life of the Beach Boys is the subject of two [[television film|made-for-television films]]: ''Summer Dreams: The Story of the Beach Boys'' (1990) and ''[[The Beach Boys: An American Family]]'' (2000). [[Love & Mercy (film)|''Love & Mercy'']] is a 2014 [[biographical film|biopic]] that dramatizes Brian Wilson during his time with the Beach Boys.{{citation needed|date=June 2015}}

